_:N46bac0e725f24acfbe6ee75e94f04963 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Committee on Fuel Poverty (<abbr title=\"Committee on Fuel Poverty\">CFP</abbr>) is an expert committee sponsored by the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero\">Department for Energy Security and Net Zero</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"responsibilities\">Responsibilities</h2>\n\n<p>Our role is to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>monitor and report on progress of the government’s <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/sustainable-warmth-protecting-vulnerable-households-in-england\" title=\"Sustainable warmth: protecting vulnerable households in England\">Fuel Poverty Strategy</a>\n</li>\n  <li>support and challenge the government on delivery</li>\n  <li>encourage and foster a partnership approach between government and stakeholders</li>\n  <li>work where appropriate with the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.theccc.org.uk/\">Committee on Climate Change</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"who-we-are\">Who we are</h2>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Committee on Fuel Poverty\">CFP</abbr> consists of a Chair and up to 5 members who are appointed for 3 years.</p>\n\n<p>View our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/committee-on-fuel-poverty/about/membership\">membership</a> and <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/committee-on-fuel-poverty-meeting-minutes\">meeting minutes</a>.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"establishment-of-the-cfp\">Establishment of the <abbr title=\"Committee on Fuel Poverty\">CFP</abbr>\n</h3>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Committee on Fuel Poverty\">CFP</abbr> replaces the former <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/the-fuel-poverty-advisory-group\">Fuel Poverty Advisory Group (<abbr title=\"Fuel Poverty Advisory Group\">FPAG</abbr>)</a>. This follows a triennial review of <abbr title=\"Fuel Poverty Advisory Group\">FPAG</abbr> which took place during 2014.</p>\n\n<p>In 2025 the <abbr title=\"Committee on Fuel Poverty\">CFP</abbr> changed from an non-departmental public body to an expert committee.</p>\n\n<p>See our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/committee-on-fuel-poverty-framework-document\">framework document</a>.</p>\n\n</div>" .
